{"word":"Hiram","slug":"hiram","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hiram</b> <a href=\"#/H2438\">H2438</a> <br/> 1. Called Huram, king of Tyre:<br/> - Builds a house for David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=11'>2Sa 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=14&verse=1'>1Ch 14:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=3'>2Ch 2:3</a> <br/> - Aids Solomon in building the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5'>1Ki 5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=16'>2Ch 2:16</a> <br/> - Dissatisfied with cities given by Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=13'>1Ki 9:13</a> <br/> - Makes presents of gold and seamen to Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=14'>1Ki 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=28'>1Ki 9:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=11'>1Ki 10:11</a> <br/> 2. Called Huram, an artificer sent by King Hiram to execute the artistic work of the interior of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=45'>1Ki 7:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=13'>2Ch 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=16'>2Ch 4:16</a>"}]}